I. Login page:

Username upper panel = .//input[@placeholder='Username']
Password upper panel = .//input[@placeholder='Password']
Sign In button = .//button[text()='Sign In']

Username = .//input[@id='username-register']
Email = .//input[@id='email-register']
Password = .//input[@id='password-register']
Sign up for OurApp button = .//button[@type='submit']

II. Home page:

Search button = .//a[@href='#']
Chat button = .//span[@class='text-white mr-2 header-chat-icon']
My Profile button = .//a[@class='mr-2']
Create Post button = .//a[@class='btn btn-sm btn-success mr-2']
Sign Out button = .//form[@action='/logout']

III. Creating a new post

Title field = .//input[@name='title']
Body Content = .//textarea[@name='body']
This is a unique post checkbox = .//input[@type='checkbox']
Select value dropdown = .//select[@name='select1']
Option value = .//option[@value='Group Message']
Save New Post button = .//button[@class='btn btn-primary']


IV. Edit and delete a post

Search field = .//input[@placeholder='What are you interested in?']
List of the posts in the search = .//a[@class='list-group-item list-group-item-action']
Select your post from the list = .//a[@strong='New post on Tuesday'] --- ????????????????????????????

Edit a post button = .//a[@data-original-title='Edit']
Delete a post button = .//button[@data-original-title='Delete']




